Iteration 23: h44: interstitial_lung_disease_history: effect -0.016 months, SE 0.017, z -0.95, p=0.3426. h45: heart_failure: effect -0.029 months, SE 0.011, z -2.67, p=0.0077.
Iteration 24: h46: treatment_pembrolizumab:pdl1_tps_above_median: effect 0.013 months, SE 0.013, z 1.01, p=0.3102.
